整理 |河　西截至2020年2月22日12点，在这次疫情中，累计报告的死亡病例已经达到了2348人。
As at 12: 00 p.m. on 22 February 2020, the cumulative number of reported deaths from the epidemic has reached 2,348.
这些鲜活的生命，在一次突如其来的疫情中倒下了。
These fresh lives, in a sudden outbreak of the fall.
他们中有普通人，也有院长、导演、院士、画家……很多都是各行各业中的精英，他们的离去是他们所在行业的巨大损失，怎不令人扼腕叹息。
They include ordinary people, presidents, directors, academicians, painters... many of them elites from all walks of life, and their departure is a great loss to their industry and a source of regret.
今天，让我们来缅怀这些在疫情中逝去的英才，为他们点上一支蜡烛。
Today, let us honour the memory of those who perished in the epidemic and light a candle for them.
杨晓波杨晓波（1963年1月-2020年1月27日），湖北天门人，美国俄亥俄大学工商管理硕士，1988年5月加入中国共产党，1988年6月参加工作。
Yang Xiaobo Yang (January 1963-January 27, 2020), a native of Tianmen, Hubei University, MBA, Ohio University, USA, joined the Communist Party of China in May 1988 and joined the work force in June 1988.
曾任湖北省黄石市委副书记，黄石市市长、长江财产保险股份有限公司董事长。
He was deputy secretary of Huangshi Municipal Committee, mayor of Huangshi and chairman of Changjiang Property Insurance Co. Ltd.
他曾主政黄石，带领这座矿产枯竭的三四线城市摆脱了对资源的依赖，成功实现经济转型；他亦是近期首位因感染肺炎去世的金融业高管，掌舵长江财险六年。
He led Yellowstone, the mineral-depleted third and fourth-tier city that successfully transformed its economy from dependence on resources; he was also the first financial executive to die of pneumonia in the recent past, steering the Yangtze River for six years.
2020年1月25日（大年初一），杨晓波确诊为新冠肺炎后入住湖北省人民医院，于1月27日晚上去世。
January 25, 2020 (New Year's Day), Yang Xiaobo confirmed the new crown pneumonia after the People's Hospital in Hubei Province, died on the night of January 27.
红凌红凌（1966年11月-2020年2月7日），美国亚利桑那大学生物化学博士，生前系华中科大三级教授、博士生导师、楚天学者（特聘教授），中国抗癌协会纳米肿瘤学会委员和中国稀有疾病研究联盟全国协调主任。
Red Ling Hong Ling (November 1966-7 February 2020), Ph.D. Biochemistry, University of Arizona, former Professor, Ph.D. Tutor, Chu Tian Scholar (Distinguished Professor), Member of the Chinese Cancer Society Nanoma Society and National Coordinating Director of the China Rare Diseases Research Alliance.
主要研究与人体重大疾病及稀有疾病相关的基因UBIAD1的分子机制。
The molecular mechanism of UBIAD 1, a gene associated with major and rare diseases in humans, is studied.
2020年2月7日，红凌不幸因新冠病毒感染，医治无效在协和医院去世，享年54岁。
On February 7, 2020, Hong Ling died at Concorde Hospital at the age of 54 due to a new crown virus infection.
林正斌林正斌（1957年7月-2020年2月10日），中国知名移植专家，华中科技大学同济医学院附属同济医院器官移植科原副主任医师。
Lin Zhengbin Lin Zhengbin (July 1957-February 10, 2020), a renowned Chinese transplant specialist, former deputy director of organ transplant department of Tongji Hospital affiliated with Tongji Medical School, HUST.
林正斌在肾移植术及术后治疗、慢性移植肾肾病的治疗、肾移植术后的各种并发症的处理具有丰富的临床经验，其主持的《国产环孢素赛斯平的实验及临床研究》曾荣获湖北省卫生厅科技进步一等奖。
Lin Zhengbin has rich clinical experience in kidney transplantation and postoperative treatment, treatment of chronic renal transplantation nephropathy and management of complications after renal transplantation.
2020年2月10日上午11点，林正斌教授因新冠肺炎抢救无效不幸逝世。
At 11 a.m. on February 10, 2020, Professor Lin Zhengbin died of pneumonia.
刘寿祥刘寿祥（1958年4月-2020年2月13日），湖北武汉人，毕业于湖北艺术学院美术系师范专业，曾为中国美术家协会水彩艺术委员会副秘书长，湖北美术学院美术教育系原主任、教授、硕士生导师。
Liu Shouxiang Liu Shouxiang (April 1958-February 13, 2020), a native of Hubei Province, graduated from the Faculty of Fine Arts of Hubei Institute of Art. He was Deputy Secretary-General of the Watercolor Arts Committee of the Chinese Artists' Association.
刘寿祥擅长水彩画，作品多次参加全国美展，并被中国美术馆、上海美术馆、江苏省美术馆、深圳美术馆等收藏。
Liu Shouxiang is good at watercolor paintings. His works have participated in many national art exhibitions and have been collected by the Chinese Art Museum, Shanghai Art Museum, Jiangsu Art Museum, Shenzhen Art Museum, etc.
作品有《牧牛少年》 《桥》等。
Works include "Cowherd Boy" and "Bridge" and so on.
2020年2月13日，刘寿祥因新冠肺炎逝世，享年62岁。
Liu died of pneumonia on February 13, 2020 at the age of 62.
刘筱娴刘筱娴（1933年5月-2020年2月13日），中国著名预防医学教育家、妇幼卫生专业创始人，全国五一劳动奖章获得者。
Liu Xiaoxian Liu Xiaoxian (May 1933-February 13, 2020), China's renowned preventive medicine educator, mother and child health professional founder, the National Labor Medal recipient.
出生于广州市，祖籍广东台山，1957年毕业并留在武汉医学院（现同济医学院）卫生系任教。
Born in Guangzhou, Guangdong Taishan ancestor, graduated in 1957 and remained in Wuhan Medical School (now Tongji Medical College) Department of Health teaching.
华中科技大学同济医学院公共卫生学院教授、研究生导师。
Professor and Postgraduate Tutor, School of Public Health, Tongji Medical School, CUHK.
2020年2月13日，因病医治无效不幸在武汉同济医院逝世，享年87岁。
On 13 February 2020, he died at the Tongji Hospital in Wuhan, aged 87, as a result of ineffective medical treatment.
常凯常凯（？-2020年2月14日），湖北电影制片厂导演、“像音像”对外联络部原主任。
Changkaikai (? - Feb. 14, 2020), director of Hubei Film Studio and former director of the "Like Audio-Visual" Foreign Liaison Department.
他所从事的“像音像”是推进戏曲振兴的国家文化工程，主要致力于将戏曲名家演绎的经典剧目以尽可能完美的影像资料形式加以保护和传承，曾参与电影《我的渡口》、楚剧《可怜天下父母心》等作品的拍摄制作。
He is engaged in the "like audio-visual" is the national cultural project to promote the revival of opera, mainly dedicated to the opera artists interpretation of classical repertoire in the form of the best possible image of the form of information, and has participated in the film "My Ferry," Chu opera "pathetic parents.
2020年2月14日，常凯因新冠肺炎医治无效，在武汉市黄陂区去世，享年55岁。
On February 14, 2020, Changkai died of Huangpi District, Wuhan, aged 55, for failing to treat his new crown pneumonia.
在这次疫情中，常凯一家遭遇灭顶之灾。
In this outbreak, the Changkai family suffered the disaster.
1月25日大年初一，常凯的父亲发烧咳嗽，呼吸困难，送至多家医院就治，均告无床位接收，多方求助，也还是一床难求，被迫回家自救。
January 25, the New Year's Day, Changkai's father has a fever and cough, breathing difficulties, sent to a number of hospitals on the treatment, are admitted to no beds, or many help, or a bed, forced to return home to help themselves.
1月27日，常凯的父亲去世。
On January 27, Changkai's father died.
2月2日，常凯的母亲去世。
On February 2, Changkai's mother died.
2月14日，常凯和他的姐姐同天去世。
On February 14, Changkai and his sister died the same day.
他的姐姐就是湖北省武汉市武昌医院梨园街社区卫生服务中心注射室护士柳帆。
His sister is Liu Fan, a nurse in the injection room of Li Yuan Street Community Health Center, Wuchang Hospital, Wuhan, Hubei Province.
2020年2月14日18:30，柳帆因患新冠肺炎在全力抢救后无效病逝，享年59岁。
At 18: 30 on February 14, 2020, Willow died of New Crown Pneumonia at the age of 59.
短短17天，常凯家中4人相继离世。
In just 17 days, four people died in Changkai's family.
段正澄段正澄（1934年6月-2020年2月15日），出生于江苏省镇江市。
Duan Zhengcheng Cheng Cheng Cheng (June 1934-February 15, 2020) was born in Zhenjiang City, Jiangsu Province.
1957年从华中工学院（现华中科技大学）机械系毕业后留校任教，先后担任机械系助教、讲师、副教授，教研室副主任、主任；教授、博士生导师、制造自动化研究所所长、制造装备数字化国家工程研究中心首席科学家。
1957 After graduating from the Department of Mechanics, Central China Institute of Technology (now Huazhong University of Science and Technology), he served as assistant, lecturer, associate professor, assistant director and director of the teaching and research department.
他长期从事机械制造与自动化学科的教学与科研工作，研发了国际首台全身伽马刀，为湖北的经济发展和科技进步做出了突出贡献。
He has long been engaged in the teaching and research of mechanical manufacturing and automation. He has developed the first gamma knife in the world, and made outstanding contributions to Hubei's economic development and scientific and technological progress.
2009年当选为中国工程院院士。
Elected member of the Chinese Academy of Engineering in 2009.
2020年2月15日，因患新型冠状病毒肺炎在医院逝世，享年86岁。
February 15, 2020, the new coronavirus pneumonia died in hospital, at the age of 86.
刘智明刘智明（1969年-2020年2月18日），湖北十堰人，毕业于武汉大学医学院，主任医师、博士、神经外科专家，生前系武汉市武昌医院院长。
Liu Zhiming (1969-February 18, 2020), Hubei Shiyan, a graduate of Wuhan University School of Medicine, director of physician, doctor, neurosurgeon, former director of Wuhan Wuchang Hospital.
擅长颅脑外伤、颅内肿瘤、脑血管病及椎管内病的诊断和治疗，特别擅长神经外科疾病手术治疗。
Specializes in the diagnosis and treatment of craniocerebral trauma, intracranial neoplasms, cerebrovascular diseases and intravertebral canal diseases, especially in the surgical treatment of neurosurgical diseases.
2020年2月18日上午10点30分，刘智明因感染新冠肺炎去世。
Liu Zhiming died of pneumonia on February 18, 2020 at 10: 30 am.
柯卉兵柯卉兵（1979年2月-2020年2月19日），出生于湖北黄梅，曾任华中科技大学社会学院教授、工会主席。
Conduit soldier (Feb. 1979-Feb. 19, 2020), born in Huangmei, Hubei Province, was a professor of Social Sciences, Huazhong University of Science and Technology and President of the Trade Union.
2月19日凌晨，柯卉兵因患新冠肺炎不幸逝世，年仅41岁。
In the early morning hours of February 19, she died of pneumonia, at the age of 41.
柯卉兵致力于中国社会福利政策研究，主持国家社科基金项目2项、华中科技大学自主创新基金项目、华中科技大学“教学质量工程”教学研究项目，参与教育部哲学社会科学重大课题攻关项目、国家社科基金一般项目、教育部人文社会科学重点研究基地重大项目等多项国家和省部级课题的研究。
Conhui devoted to the study of social welfare policy in China, presided over 2 projects of the National Social Science Fund, conducted projects of self-innovation project of Huazhong University of Science and Technology, teaching and research project of "Teaching Quality Project" of Huazhong University of Technology.
曾任中国社会学会社会发展与社会保障专业委员会理事兼秘书长、中国社会保障30人论坛青年学者联盟成员、中国社会保障学会青年委员会委员。
He was a member of the Professional Committee on Social Development and Social Security of the Chinese Sociological Association, a member of the Young Scholars' Union of the 30-member China Social Security Forum and a member of the Youth Committee of the China Social Security Society.
在本次疫情中，华中科技大学也是重灾区，近半个月来，华中科技大学已有5位教授因患新冠肺炎离世。
In this outbreak, Huazhong University of Science and Technology is also a major disaster area, nearly half a month, Huazhong University of Science and Technology has five professors died of pneumonia.
他们分别是：红凌、林正斌、刘筱娴、段正澄和柯卉兵。
They are: Hong Ling, Lin Zhengbin, Liu Xiaoxian, Duan Zhengcheng and Conhui soldiers.
征集令《新民周刊》现面向全国征集新冠肺炎采访对象和真实故事：如果你是参与抗击新冠肺炎疫情的医护人员或其家属，我们希望聆听你的“战疫”故事，也希望传达你的诉求。
Call for orders The New People's Weekly is now soliciting interviews and true stories from all over the country: If you are a healthcare worker or family member involved in the fight against the outbreak, we hope to hear your "epidemic" story and convey your message.
如果你是确诊、疑似患者本人或家属，我们希望了解你和家人如何“抗疫”的过程，让外界了解你的真实经历。
If you are a confirmed, suspected patient or family member, we would like to know how you and your family have responded to the epidemic and let the outside world know about your true experience.
如果你是疫情严重地区的普通市民，我们希望展现你的乐观，并倾听你所需的帮助。
If you are an ordinary citizen of a highly affected area, we hope to show your optimism and listen to the help you need.
如果你是公共服务人员或各类捐助者，我们希望看到你的“最美逆行”，记录下你的无私。
If you are a public service provider or a variety of donors, we want to see your "most beautiful retrograde" and record your selflessness.
……抗击新冠肺炎疫情，我们诚征对疫情了解的社会各界人士，提供相关线索，说出你的故事，让我们用新闻留存这一切。
To fight the New Crown Pneumonia epidemic, we sincerely invite all sectors of the community to understand the epidemic, provide relevant clues, tell your story, let us use the news to retain all this.
